<bibRefCitation author="Belokobylskij, SA" journalOrPublisher="Far Eastern Entomologist" pageId="0" pageNumber="133" pagination="89 - 124" refId="B4" refString="Belokobylskij, SA, 2000a. New species of the subfamily Euphorinae (Hymenoptera, Braconidae) from East Palaearctic. Part IV. Far Eastern Entomologist 90: 89 - 124" title="New species of the subfamily Euphorinae (Hymenoptera, Braconidae) from East Palaearctic. Part IV." volume="90" year="2000 a">Belokobylskij 2000a</bibRefCitation>
