<bibRefCitation author="Papp, J" journalOrPublisher="Acta Zoologica Academiae Scientiarum Hungaricae" pageId="0" pageNumber="133" pagination="115 - 152" refId="B22" refString="Papp, J, 2003. Braconidae (Hymenoptera) from Korea, XXI. Species of fifteen subfamilies. Acta Zoologica Academiae Scientiarum Hungaricae 49: 115 - 152" title="Braconidae (Hymenoptera) from Korea, XXI. Species of fifteen subfamilies." volume="49" year="2003">Papp (2003)</bibRefCitation>
